The script to visualize and do analysis of 3D data from koral
simext3d.py made by D.Abarca and improved by D. Lancova and corrections by F.Kayanikhoo for neutron star case
slice_with_vectors_fast.py and myinterpole.py made by D. Gronkiewicz 

To run you can use --help
