  xlabel = f"${slice_name[0].lower()}\,[GM/c^2]$"
/home/fatima/Documents/3dtest/slice_with_vectors_fast.py:133: SyntaxWarning: invalid escape sequence '\,'
  ylabel = f"${slice_name[1].lower()}\,[GM/c^2]$"
usage: slice_with_vectors_fast.py [-h] [--resolution RESOLUTION] [--span SPAN]
                                  [--scalar SCALAR [SCALAR ...]]
                                  [--vector VECTOR [VECTOR ...]]
                                  [--slice SLICE [SLICE ...]]
                                  d

3D slice visualization

positional arguments:
  d                     Input data file

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --resolution RESOLUTION
                        Grid resolution (default: 512)
  --span SPAN           Grid span (default: 500)
  --scalar SCALAR [SCALAR ...]
                        Scalar field name(s) (default: rho)
  --vector VECTOR [VECTOR ...]
                        Vector field name(s) (default: bcon)
  --slice SLICE [SLICE ...]
                        Slice plane(s): two letters from X,Y,Z optionally followed by
                        offset (default: XZ)